Usage: addNet [-help] [-bus <msb:lsb>] { <netName> } [ -moduleBased <moduleName> ] [-power | -ground ]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<netName>                     # Name of Net (string, required)
-bus <msb:lsb>                # Bit range for bus nets (string, optional)
-ground                       # Create a ground net (bool, optional)
-moduleBased <moduleName>     # Name of verilog module
                              # ((vCell|topCell), optional)
-power                        # Create a power net (bool, optional)